topIssues.title: DM stopped working in Discord (latest version 1.4.4.)
topIssues.author: harperaa
topIssues.body:
**Describe the bug**

Latest update, perhaps sooner, broke DM in discord.

**To Reproduce**

DM a bot in discord, it won't work, no response.

**Expected behavior**

This worked prior, I think I was on 1.4.1 before I updated, but can't remember.
